    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.1.2-provision1",
      "type": "provision",
      "section": "26.1.2",
      "text": "The design wind loads for buildings and other structures, including the MWFRS and C&C elements thereof, shall be determined using one of the procedures as specified in this section. An outline of the overall procedure for the determination of the wind loads, including design references, is provided in Figure 26.1-1.",
