      "text": "3. Directional Procedure for building appurtenances (rooftop structures and rooftop equipment) and other structures (such as solid freestanding walls and solid freestanding signs, chimneys, tanks, open signs, single-plane frames, and trussed towers) as specified in Chapter 29; or",
      "cross_references": [
